admin.php
    Allows administrator to
        authorize users to rent
        delete or create arbitrary reservations
        add, remove, or change aircraft records
        add, remove, or change type records
    Not accessible to users who aren't administrators

account.php
    Allows user to
        Change any part of their account (username, password, name, etc.)

scheduler.php
    Displays schedule for an aircraft for the week
    Allows user to schedule an aircraft

menu
    remove "View Flights"

db
    add is_admin field to Pilot db
